public class GAApplication
extends javax.swing.JFrame

A GAApplication object gives a Graphical User Interface to the GAStrategy framework.

GAApplication is to be viewed with respect to the Model-View-Controller pattern. GAApplication provides a way through which tools can be added to enchance the usability and view-ability of the GAStrategy framework.

GAApplication can be instantiated via the command-line interface java GAApplication or java GAApplication FitnessFunction GAIndividual

Version:
1.0
Author:
Pat Burke, Ryan Dixon, Jake Good, Jayapal Prabakaran
